reviewText: Worth anything more than $3? Heck no! The DVD is only about 10 mins long, if even that. But my son is 5, has owned this DVD for years, and can still watch it non-stop on loop for over an hour. Our 1 year old daughter is addicted to it as well. I think it's the beginning song that makes it so catchy. I wish they made more of these DVDs.
